%F A028174 a(n) = (2*10^(n+2)-3*9^(n+2)+2*6^(n+2)-5^(n+2))/4. - _Yahia Kahloune_, Jun 03 2013
%F A028174 a(0)=1, a(1)=30, a(2)=571, a(3)=8820, a(n) = 30*a(n-1)-329*a(n-2)+1560*a(n-3)-2700*a(n-4). - _Harvey P. Dale_, Nov 07 2013
%F A028174 a(n) = 6^(n+1)-5^(n+1)+19*a(n-1)-90*a(n-2). - _Vincenzo Librandi_, Jul 16 2026
%t A028174 CoefficientList[Series[1/((1-5x)(1-6x)(1-9x)(1-10x)),{x,0,20}],x] (* _Harvey P. Dale_, Nov 07 2013 *)
